{"tid":1991511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腐敗制度養大警暴巨獸 醫護親聽「做咩剝晒我啲衫？」","createTime":"2020-04-27T12:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T17:31:25.000Z","uid":105340,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c867b8fb720bde507ad179349206153dc23799e2","tid":1991511,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/LOLT4RKCE2T4JLHRGQMAFMX7OM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR2X7uxSUJXi5I2ZBDEgGRMs8jQLZUhjfsWEbWNdlTmAZMdoJlUWA3NcI94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2FLOLT4RKCE2T4JLHRGQMAFMX7OM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR2X7uxSUJXi5I2ZBDEgGRMs8jQLZUhjfsWEbWNdlTmAZMdoJlUWA3NcI94&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4aooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=ff1b8939\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2FLOLT4RKCE2T4JLHRGQMAFMX7OM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR2X7uxSUJXi5I2ZBDEgGRMs8jQLZUhjfsWEbWNdlTmAZMdoJlUWA3NcI94&h=a70f6183\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/LOLT4RKCE2T4JLHRGQMAFMX7OM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR2X7uxSUJXi5I2ZBDEgGRMs8jQLZUhjfsWEbWNdlTmAZMdoJlUWA3NcI94</a><br />\n除左憤怒 仲可以做D咩<br />\n<br />\n被捕醫護阿仁 親聽「做咩剝晒我啲衫？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰●專題】邵家臻「濫用私刑無制衡」 還柙人士被警恐嚇「搞全家」<br />\n<br />\n理大圍城首天，51名醫護及記者雙手被反扣於背後坐在地上被捕的相片，令人震怒，阿仁（化名）是其中的一名醫護，被捕後所經歷的，令他患上創傷後遺症，要服藥和定時覆診，那一夜，發生了他沒法想像的事。<br />\n<br />\n他曾於公立醫院專科門診任職醫護人員，11月17日晚上，他在理大附近疏導正在離開的市民，突然有一隊防暴警用槍指向他，然後衝向他、把他按在地上用警棍打他，阿仁身形健碩，捱了幾棍不算甚麼，但言語上的侮辱，他卻無法啞忍。醫護輪着被搜身，一名督察對他說：「你呢啲死曱甴，留喺世上有咩用。」他忍不住回應一句：「唔該你面對住自己套制服同人格，講嘢講得清楚啲、乾淨少少，唔好貶低自己、矮化自己嘅種族。」<br />\n<br />\n然後，這名督察竟然從附近拾起一支汽油彈，對他說：「你哋啱啱掉呢支嘢嘛，依家還返畀你。」正想把汽油彈塞進阿仁的背包，但背包已裝滿東西沒有位置，早前的搜身過程亦一直有錄影，證明袋中沒有任何汽油彈，「指揮官見到呢個情況，對佢喝止，其他同事亦制止咗佢，所以先無成功插贓嫁禍！」<br />\n<br />\n在警署拘留期間，被捕者被打至頭破血流的畫面，當然不會缺乏。「唔少示威者被打到頭爆，被幾個警員拖行，佢已無晒知覺。亦有人血流滿面無晒意識，警員一面拖住佢，一面用棍打佢塊面，叫佢咪扮嘢起身行」。<br />\n昏迷繼續打 羞辱聲不絕<br />\n<br />\n即使自己並非示威者，在警署內亦絕不好受，被捕10小時後有警員問他何時願意錄口供，他說想見律師，「佢用警棍不斷喺我身上下搓動施壓，話有嘢講就好講，唔講就留返拜山先講」。警署內他們再次被搜身，因為太多被捕人士，沒有足夠的搜身房間和拘留室，所以只能在一間大房內，以黑色木板隔成小區，他知道同時間有人被搜身、有人被打、有人正在見律師，全沒私隱可言，突然一聲女孩的尖叫，令他毛骨悚然。<br />\n<br />\n「個女仔大嗌：『做咩剝晒我啲衫？做咩摸我？』佢大聲尖叫同喊。」阿仁感慨，即使聽見女孩被羞辱的聲音，或是眼看最少五、六人被打至滿頭是血，肢體呈紫色及滲血，當時「肉隨砧板上」，根本愛莫能助，「佢哋已昏迷，我肯定佢哋腦已受創，打極都唔醒，點解已昏迷都仲要打？打到佢哋骨折！」有警員甚至在他面前戲謔：「呢度成班醫護啊，唔使去醫院喇！慳返！」<br />\n我地每次有手足被人捉 所有撚狗人士都只係退走<br />\n唔係救人<br />\n我唔係前線 無資格講<br />\n只係講 被捕無論係唔係和理非 既女仔 都會比人強姦<br />\n只係果個唔係你仔女"},{"pid":"5d04bb2e05fb147cedccb14607820910d9f5502e","tid":1991511,"uid":119188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"保持憤怒"},{"pid":"e823f290ac0c5124eb448de3ae8ac01bd5bf6ddb","tid":1991511,"uid":105340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d04bb2e05fb147cedccb14607820910d9f5502e","tid":1991511,"uid":119188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"保持憤怒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"之後呢<br />\n真係無力感啦"},{"pid":"458c92dd4b63e302b89d73fcfd6c22666d9c98d0","tid":1991511,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaf5061b13f113c1f185c127fa4a6c79b368eb8","tid":1991511,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"775b2cdd2b5afb97e50ed0a8b27ee99eaa713e71","tid":1991511,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eec878a04cc1d2cbf122cdb94d336fa81f0cd21","tid":1991511,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"a800a39ad431ba24ceb437205a98b4ced0f915e8","tid":1991511,"uid":38175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔：今日要100%和理非 警署要安然無羔"},{"pid":"fb8c4de152a299e72755d1d72545eca5be7e3a55","tid":1991511,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c7f55f765c2e18a5f41d6af53019b7d098df7f","tid":1991511,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點做？"},{"pid":"40c008fb7d905e3907ac4f2d6f9189cfcd133a9b","tid":1991511,"uid":105340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"中大831 吳同學宜家唔知去左邊<br />\n無晒消息<br />\n仲有好多夜晚出左街就比狗擄走既女手足 都失蹤<br />\n應該都兇多吉少<br />\n我唔後生 就30歲 無勇氣前線<br />\n真係靠錢去支援手足"},{"pid":"a43c32022e7cc4521292d5094c645d84b9dc8f16","tid":1991511,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58c7f55f765c2e18a5f41d6af53019b7d098df7f","tid":1991511,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n出手太遲"},{"pid":"3edcd595ef16000232d4f6e8bf8da758254ff871","tid":1991511,"uid":77717,"like":0,"